It hurts... Mother...

387
00:41:16,070 --> 00:41:19,110
What do we do now?

388
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,880
Father...

389
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:41,990
You're wounded. Lie down.

390
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:46,530
Zhixing...

391
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:54,980
The weight of the Zhuang family will now fall to you.

392
00:41:56,590 --> 00:42:00,250
How can I be worthy of that?

393
00:42:00,250 --> 00:42:04,700
Yesterday, you saved the entire family.

394
00:42:05,700 --> 00:42:08,510
You're not just a good son,

395
00:42:09,420 --> 00:42:14,070
you'll make a great general one day.

396
00:42:14,820 --> 00:42:16,720
Father...

397
00:42:17,740 --> 00:42:21,190
