398
00:42:21,190 --> 00:42:28,010
Last night, why did Cao Jingxian suddenly attack you?

399
00:42:29,510 --> 00:42:36,700
Don't ask. One day, I'll tell you everything.

400
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:38,950
For now, focus on recovering.

